title: Dragon Ball FighterZ - Official World Tour 2023/2024 Announcement Trailer
description:
Watch the announcement trailer for the Dragon Ball FighterZ World Tour 2023/2024. Seven qualifying tournaments called 'Power Events' will be held around the world. Champions from each of these tournaments will receive a Dragon Ball Trophy and earn a spot to compete in the Finals. The tour will begin at EVO 2023 in Las Vegas, Nevada, running from August 4-6, 2023. Brace yourself for the ultimate clash of power and skill when the Dragon Ball FighterZ World Tour returns.
